@host = http://localhost:5181

### Connexion (récupère un JWT)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@moneta.fr",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Liste des factures
GET {{host}}/api/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Liste des clients
GET {{host}}/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Création d'un client
POST {{host}}/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Boulangerie Léon",
  "email": "compta@boulangerie-leon.fr",
  "siret": "56202000000047",
  "address": { "line1": "5 place du Marché", "postalCode": "69001", "city": "Lyon" }
}
